ource/Anthony_Boucher\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The X thread was the latest salvo in a dispute between Musk and Grimes which has seen her and her mother use X, the platform Musk owns, to reach him.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Grimes\", \"score\": 0.99999999995498, \"rank\": 4.449810388481998e-11, \"text\": \"Grimes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Grimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Grimes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The thread opens, \\\"Dear Elon@elonmuskIt was nice seeing you on Father's Day.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope you got the card that I helped X make.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was so proud of it.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am writing here as the only way I have to reach you.\\\"\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As you know, my 93 year old mother is now at end-of-life palliative care,\\\" Garossino continues.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She yearns to see and hold Claire's children one last time.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially the youngest, whom she has not yet met.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was thrilled for the kids' planned visit to celebrate her birthday this weekend.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But those hopes were crushed when the trip was canceled.\\\"\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dear Elon@elonmuskIt was nice seeing you on Father's Day.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope you got the card that I helped X make.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was so proud of it.I am writing here as the only way I have to reach you.As you know, my 93 year old mother is now at end-of-life palliative care.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Musk is currently at the Paris Olympics, although it is unconfirmed if X is with him too.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was not seen with Musk on Friday night, butthe moguldid post to his own X account from the ceremony.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Grimes has alsoreposted the threadon her X account.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Daily Beast reached out to Grimes and Musk for comment.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beauty_and_the_Beast\", \"score\": 0.9999963165148157, \"rank\": 3.6834987567213143e-06, \"text\": \"Beast\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beauty_and_the_Beast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beauty_and_the_Beast\"}, {\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Grimes\", \"score\": 0.99999999995498, \"rank\": 4.449810388481998e-11, \"text\": \"Grimes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Grimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Grimes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am alarmed to learn that the children cannot come as you are withholding them and their needed passport documents from Claire,\\\" Garossino added.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Garossino also warned that Musk has not informed them \\\"where are the other children, and with whom,\\\" adding that \\\"they are scheduled to be with their mother.\", \"